3. cs.RO (Robotics): Reinforcement learning is widely used in robotics, and the proposed algorithm could be applied to improve the performance of robots in various tasks.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): Reinforcement learning is also used in control systems, and the proposed algorithm could be applied to improve the control performance of systems.
